snippet.title: Cube - Gardens of Zen | Game sneak peak
snippet.description:
Sneak preview trailer of a new game to be published on www.kalydo.com
Cube - Gardens of Zen is a funny 3D puzzle game taking place on a cube shaped world. More than 80 levels in four seasons, hours of playing fun. 

Sign up for the beta at www.kalydo.com
